			<p>My journey in technology didn't start with the sleek interfaces we see today. It began in the early days of mobile, working with the fundamental building blocks of <strong>SMS and MMS development</strong> shortly after earning my Computer Science degree from the <strong>University of the Philippines</strong>.</p>

